Which Search Engine is Best for You – Bing or Google?  via @wonderoftech In a move reminiscent of the Pepsi Challenge, Bing is challenging Internet users (a/k/a people) to test which search engine they prefer. By visiting the Bing It On website, you can take the test to see which search engine produces the results most helpful for you. [note] Update: The Bing It On Challenge appears to be available only for US residents and is not available on some mobile devices.
